name: Krabby Kats
description:
The ultimate Krabby Kat game! Match-up 3 or more Krabby Kats to make them fly off the board. Clear as many of our grumpy friends off the board as possible to survive to the next level.

There are hilarious videos that can be earned by unlocking new levels. Do you have what it takes to reach level 50?

WARNING: This game is addictive!

Features:

* 50 levels to play
* Cool cat videos!
* Many different themes
* Awesome power-ups
* Many kranky kat personalities
* Soothing soundtrack

Compatibility:

* iPhone
* iPod Touch
* iPad
